implemented breaks everything,

52
00:02:00,738 --> 00:02:02,280
how can we roll back
to a point where

53
00:02:02,280 --> 00:02:03,730
we knew things were stable?

54
00:02:03,730 --> 00:02:05,620
So that's what Git does.

55
00:02:05,620 --> 00:02:09,660
And then GitHub, G-I-T
hub, is a website

56
00:02:09,660 --> 00:02:14,050
