160
00:06:56,470 --> 00:06:59,710
That's what I'm blocking
myself from seeing this.

161
00:06:59,710 --> 00:07:01,630
There we go.

162
00:07:01,630 --> 00:07:03,200
Now should be a little easier.

163
00:07:03,200 --> 00:07:07,360
There we go, global
user.name and Sharad.

164
00:07:07,360 --> 00:07:09,460
And then we're going to
do the same thing, git

165
00:07:09,460 --> 00:07:18,160
config global user.email, and
then I'll do my email address.

166
00:07:18,160 --> 00:07:21,070
And again, we're not doing
any sort of logging in

167
00:07:21,070 --> 00:07:23,180
or we're not sharing our
information publicly.

168
00:07:23,180 --> 00:07:24,730
All that's happening
is that anybody

169
00:07:24,730 --> 00:07:28,420
else who is submitting
code to this repository

170
00:07:28,420 --> 00:07:29,980
that we're going
to create, they're

171
00:07:29,980 --> 00:07:32,110
going to see any
changes I made are

172
00:07:32,110 --> 00:07:35,390
